-<HattrickData>
<UserSupporterTier> : supporterTier
Indicates which Supporter package the fetching user has, or empty if not a Supporter.
</UserSupporterTier>
-<Player>
<PlayerID> : unsigned Integer
The globally unique playerID.
</PlayerID>
-<PlayerEvents Available='Boolean'>
-<PlayerEvent>
<EventDate> : DateTime
Date and time when the event was recorded.
</EventDate>
<PlayerEventTypeID> : unsigned Integer
An identifier to show which type of event it is. No list of events will be available. Each CHPP will have to collect an eventlist him-/herself.
</PlayerEventTypeID>
<EventText> : String (HTML encoded)
The description of the event, as shown in the HTML-output. May contain HTML-tags.
</EventText>
</PlayerEvent>
</PlayerEvents>
</Player>
